data.description: You are going to love this home in well sought out Black Oak neighborhood.! So much love and care from original owners devoted to this 4 bed, 2.5 bath home with 2 furnaces. Large entryway leads you to the living room, bedrooms to the left and kitchen & family room to the right.  Lots of triple pane windows to keep the home bright and roomie. Formal dining space right off kitchen and breakfast nook at the other end with added Cedar cabinetry. 400 square foot addition with sky light has been added to an already large Rec room with wet bar and bay window. Laundry enclosed off this room as well. Additional smoke detectors and fan in attic. Cabinets stay in the oversized garage. 63 ft beautiful deck wraps the back of the house. Yard treatment has been paid thru 2023. Seller to offer Home Warranty Advantage Plus at closing. Close to shopping, parks, restaurants, schools, and highways.
